TestFrame 1.0

This testing framework is very transparent, and we believe it will also be more transparent to artificial intelligence.

Packages
Package
Description
org.testframe.api
Provides annotations and an assertions library for test authors.
org.testframe.engine
Executes tests. Note that for the time being this is limited to the command line, no integration with integrated development environments (IDEs) is provided yet.
